frames.caption: A person lies in bed under a heavy blanket in a rustic room with a view of an industrial landscape through the window. The room is dimly lit by a small stove, casting a warm glow on the stone walls and wooden furniture. Outside, smoke billows from factory chimneys, contrasting with the tranquility inside.
frames.description: The scene is set in a rustic, dimly lit bedroom with a view of an industrial area through the window. The room features stone walls, wooden beams, and minimal furnishings, creating a cozy yet somber atmosphere.
